text.section:
A person may not be a member of the committee if:
The person is an officer, employee, or paid consultant of a Kentucky trade association in the field of surgical assisting;
The person's spouse is an officer, manager, or paid consultant of a Kentucky trade association in the field of surgical assisting;
The person is a registered lobbyist for compensation on behalf of a profession related to the field of surgical assisting; or
The person is presently subject to a disciplinary order issued by their licensing or certifying body.
